    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You know one extra cantrip from the Druid spell list, and your Druid spells deal additional damage and healing equal to your current maximum number of Wild Shapes as shown in the Wild Shape column of the Druid Features table. In addition, your mystical connection to nature gives you a bonus to your Intelligence (Arcana or Nature) checks. The bonus equals your Wisdom modifier (minimum bonus of +1, currently @abilities.wis.mod).</p><section class=\"secret\" id=\"secret-rQLzhWqeAbR9AAZH\"><p><strong>Foundry Note</strong></p><p>This feature includes an Active Effect which automates the increase to your known cantrips and the bonus to your Arcana and Nature checks. It also adds your Wild Shape count to <strong>all</strong> melee and ranged spell damage, so for your non-Druid spells you will have to subtract it.  It does not automate the additional healing.</p></section>",
